snippet.title: Brick Odyssey Trailer - Indie Roguelike Coming Out Soon
snippet.description:
My first creation as a solo dev, the game will be available on Steam in early 2023.
Wether you feel like adding it to your wishlist, joining the discord, or writing your thoughts in a comment, I appreciate all feedback and will gladly answer any questions.

Steam Page : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2211110/Brick_Odyssey/
Discord Server : https://discord.gg/wTQ5h4Jp7Y
